            "title": "Comparing methods to estimate the proportion of turbine-induced bird and bat mortality in the search area under a road and pad search protocol",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Joseph Duggan",
                    "lastName": "Maurer"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
