            "title": "Endocranial Cast Anatomy of the Extinct Hipposiderid Bats Palaeophyllophora and Hipposideros (Pseudorhinolophus) (Mammalia: Chiroptera)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
